{"tid":57453,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"叫凍華田凍呵叻仲要少冰是咪岸鳩","createTime":"2016-12-28T04:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T00:14:09.000Z","uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d45996d7332ce02b6459c6b520344020e6dcef32","tid":57453,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"係人都知華田呵叻呢啲即沖飲品<br />\n係要用熱水沖啲粉先溶 凍水沖就一舊舊<br />\n<br />\n之後食茶記 隔離枱叫左凍華田少冰<br />\n杯野黎到 啲冰就溶晒<br />\n杯野就唔凍唔暖 條友飲左一啖 <br />\n就叫個侍應攞返去加返啲冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗佢係唔知要用熱水沖定佢本身個人岸鳩<br />\n之前又話少冰而家又要加返啲冰<br />\n<br />\n如果我做水吧 唔加你料都偷笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該叫野之前用下個腦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759f0a6342c1a4d8123d271b67fa2cc39a06e3f8","tid":57453,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09274d9fcbeefd4461db61bb07f036999b543a1","tid":57453,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:43:37.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"514bf6137a124478d39c86517355d8745324796f","tid":57453,"uid":21527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"飲開凍奶茶走杯"},{"pid":"728a6be198a63dc9360bde2999f62f893b0ae611","tid":57453,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:00:37.000Z","msg":"OK 我無腦"},{"pid":"7d011ff3a1c7021f85da33b3a322b147f5d59118","tid":57453,"uid":17224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"睇錯凍啊叻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/